        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your understanding of your own emotions and soul deepens profoundly. You gain additional benefits depending on your current soulfeel attunement.</p>\n<p><strong>Fury:</strong> You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your Athletics checks.</p>\n<p><strong>Joy:</strong> You gain a fly Speed of 20 feet.</p>\n<p><strong>Sorrow:</strong> You gain a burrow Speed of 10 feet.</p>\n<p><strong>Wonder:</strong> You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your Perception checks.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> If you have @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Mascot Power!], the summoned minion gains the same benefits of Soulfire as you.</p>"
